I don't wanna be
"away" from it all, Dad.

19:17.920 --> 19:19.717
I like "it all"!

19:19.840 --> 19:23.435
Look, Maxie, we're using
the same map me and my dad used.

19:23.560 --> 19:26.199
We'll take the same route,
and make the same stops...

19:26.320 --> 19:28.311
and see the same sights.

19:28.440 --> 19:31.716
- But that trip would take weeks, Dad!
- Exactly!

19:31.840 --> 19:34.718
- Gettin' there is half the fun.
- Put the map away, Dad.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.637
- It's not gonna happen. I'm tellin' ya...
- Be careful, son.

19:36.760 --> 19:40.196
You'll wrinkle my past.
Ayuk! And our future.

19:40.320 --> 19:44.029
What the map says, Max,
we will follow.

19:44.160 --> 19:46.469
That's very mystical
and everything, Dad,

19:46.600 --> 19:49.512
but, uh, seriously, there's this party
I have to go to, see?

19:49.640 --> 19:52.359
- And there's this girl...
- Oh, there'll be plenty of time
for parties when you're older.

19:52.480 --> 19:55.950
Why, when I was your age
I'd never even been invited to a party.

19:56.080 --> 19:58.719
- Look at me now!
- Great, Dad.

19:58.840 --> 20:01.070
- Hop in, Maxie.
- No!

20:04.160 --> 20:06.071
All right, then.

20:06.200 --> 20:09.317
Guess I'll just have to go...
all alone.

20:09.440 --> 20:11.192
That's all.

20:11.320 --> 20:15.359
Just sit in the boat...
all alone...

20:15.480 --> 20:17.277
and talk to myself.

20:17.400 --> 20:20.676
- All alone.
- I guess so.

20:20.800 --> 20:22.916
- Oh, come on! Hop in!
- No, Dad.

20:23.040 --> 20:25.270
- Just hop right in there.
- No.

20:25.400 --> 20:28.198
- Come on, Maxie. Go for it!
- Agh! No.

20:28.320 --> 20:30.754
Let's buckle you up!

20:30.880 --> 20:32.836
And we're ready
for takeoff!

20:35.120 --> 20:36.917
Set for adventure,
Maxie?

20:37.040 --> 20:39.508
Why are you doing this
to me, Dad?

20:39.640 --> 20:42.632
'Cause I don't want ya
to end up in the electric chair.

20:42.760 --> 20:45.035
Electric chair?
What are you...

20:45.160 --> 20:46.912
I'm not givin' up
on ya, son.

20:47.040 --> 20:48.996
Together, we're gonna
work this out.

20:49.120 --> 20:50.917
Work this out?
But, Dad!

20:51.040 --> 20:53.429
No buts about it,
Maxie boy.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.630
- Your ol' pop knows best.
- But...

20:59.160 --> 21:02.232
Goodbye, house.
Goodbye, mailbox.

21:03.840 --> 21:05.751
Goodbye,
pile of broken wood.

21:07.880 --> 21:10.997
Goodbye, hopes.
Goodbye, dreams.

21:11.120 --> 21:13.998
Goodbye, Roxanne.
Roxanne!

21:14.120 --> 21:16.759
Dad, I gotta stop somewhere first.
I have to talk to someone.

21:16.880 --> 21:19.553
- Well...
- Turn here!

21:19.680 --> 21:22.752
D- Dad, watch out!

21:22.880 --> 21:26.077
Stop here.
Here! Pull over!

21:26.200 --> 21:29.988
Now, make it quick, Maxie boy.
We gotta put some road behind us.

21:30.120 --> 21:35.433
You get and cancel your first date
in less than an hour.

21:35.560 --> 21:37.516
Must be some kind of lame-o record.

21:39.680 --> 21:42.114
Grrr.

21:42.240 --> 21:44.435
Hi. Is Roxanne home?

21:44.560 --> 21:45.913
Grrr.

21:46.040 --> 21:49.112
M-M-My name's Max.

21:49.240 --> 21:51.879
Does Roxanne live here?

21:52.000 --> 21:54.798
- Does she even live
on this block? Ha-ha.
- Wait!

21:54.920 --> 21:57.036
It's okay, Daddy.
Max is a friend from school.

21:59.440 --> 22:02.910
Go on. Go on.
Good Daddy.

22:03.040 --> 22:05.076
- Hey, Max.
- Hi, there.

22:05.200 --> 22:08.272
You wanna...
uh, have a seat?

22:08.400 --> 22:10.994
Hey. Uh, u-u-oh.

22:13.440 --> 22:15.590
- Grrr.
- Daddy!

22:15.720 --> 22:18.518
I promise, he'll be better behaved
when you pick me up for the party.

22:18.640 --> 22:21.598
Yeah, that's, uh,
sorta why I came by.

22:21.720 --> 22:23.517
I'm really looking
forward to it, Max.

22:23.640 --> 22:27.315
- Yeah. I was too.
- Was?

22:27.440 --> 22:30.159
You see, my dad's on this
stupid father-son kick and...

22:30.280 --> 22:32.919
Don't worry about it, Max.
It's just a dumb party.

22:33.040 --> 22:35.759
No, it's not. Roxanne,
I really wanted to go with you.

22:35.880 --> 22:38.235
- No, Max, I understand.
Really, it's okay.
- But my dad surprised me.

22:38.360 --> 22:40.157
- These things happen.
- I don't wanna go, but I have no choice.

22:40.280 --> 22:43.636
- I'm sure I can find someone else.
- Someone else?

22:43.760 --> 22:47.435
- I'll just talk to you later.
- Uh, uh, Roxanne!

22:47.560 --> 22:49.437
Uh, my dad is, uh...

22:49.560 --> 22:52.472
My dad's taking me
to the Powerline concert in L.A.

22:52.600 --> 22:56.559
Your dad's taking you clear across
the country just to see a concert?

22:56.680 --> 22:59.752
Uh, well, you see, uh,
my dad...

22:59.880 --> 23:02.394
uh, knew... knows,
knows Powerline.

23:02.520 --> 23:04.317
They used to play together
in a band!

23:04.440 --> 23:06.556
- Yeah!
- Come on, son!

23:06.680 --> 23:09.148
Let's get this show
on the road!

23:09.280 --> 23:11.077
Uh, ha!
Just a minute!

23:11.200 --> 23:14.272
You... party animal,
you.

23:17.320 --> 23:20.517
- You're really serious.
- Absolutely.

23:20.640 --> 23:22.437
So, uh,

23:22.560 --> 23:25.552
you aren't still thinkin'
of goin' with someone else, are you?

23:25.680 --> 23:28.592
- Well, I guess...
- Because I was hopin'...

23:28.720 --> 23:31.075
I could, uh,
wave to you onstage...

23:31.200 --> 23:33.794
when we join Powerline
for the final number.

23:33.920 --> 23:35.831
This is incredible.

23:35.960 --> 23:39.839
Well, I wouldn't miss
our date for anything that
wasn't incredible, Roxanne.

23:42.840 --> 23:45.035
Have a great time
at the concert, Max.

23:45.160 --> 23:47.720
I'll see you on TV!

23:47.840 --> 23:50.593
Ah. I'm in deep sludge.

23:59.640 --> 24:02.552
Day one.
Well, here we are,

24:02.680 --> 24:06.116
out on the open road,
retracin' the steps of my boyhood.

24:06.240 --> 24:09.471
And here's Maxie!

24:09.600 --> 24:12.068
Say hi, Max.

24:12.200 --> 24:15.272
- Well, how 'bout a wave?
- Not now, Dad.

24:15.400 --> 24:17.630
Ayuk! What a kidder!

24:25.800 --> 24:28.394
Fun games I used to play
with my dad.

24:28.520 --> 24:32.399
Road bingo. Twenty ques...
Aah! Hey, Maxie.

24:32.520 --> 24:34.431
Let's play a game.
You think of a name,

24:34.560 --> 24:36.232
and I'll try and guess
who it is.

24:36.360 --> 24:38.794
- Uh, man or woman?
- Oh, man.

24:38.920 --> 24:42.276
A man, huh?
Hmm, that's a toughie.

24:42.400 --> 24:44.709
Uh, let's see.

24:44.840 --> 24:46.637
- Walt Disney!
- Right.

24:46.760 --> 24:49.797
I'm good at this.
Now, uh, I'll think of one.

24:49.920 --> 24:52.195
Hmm.

24:54.160 --> 24:56.958
Oh! You wanna
sing a song, huh?

24:57.080 --> 25:00.470
Me and my dad used to sing
this one all the time.

25:00.600 --> 25:02.989
# High hopes #

