# Oops... #

25:33.600 --> 25:37.832
Oh, g-great, Dad.
Now we don't have any music!

25:37.960 --> 25:39.837
Oh, Maxie.
It's not so bad.

25:39.960 --> 25:41.837
We'll just have
to entertain ourselves!

