29:09.920 --> 29:11.672
Grandpa!
Grandpa!

29:14.240 --> 29:17.312
Dad, you're gonna get us killed!

29:17.440 --> 29:20.432
- Why don't you just give me the map?
- Oh, no thanks, son.

29:20.560 --> 29:22.755
Navigating's
a big responsibility.

29:22.880 --> 29:26.350
Besides, you wouldn't wanna
spoil the big surprise!

29:26.480 --> 29:29.438
I'm takin' you someplace
pretty special.

29:36.280 --> 29:39.238
Gosh! It's even better
than I remembered.

29:39.360 --> 29:42.750
No, Mommy! I don't wanna go!

29:42.880 --> 29:44.791
Yeah, fun.
Tell you what.

29:44.920 --> 29:47.070
- I'm just gonna wait
right here in the car.

29:47.200 --> 29:50.909
You party pooper! Come on.
This is gonna be fun!

29:51.040 --> 29:53.679
Oh, howdy there,
folks.

29:53.800 --> 29:56.633
Lester's is proud
to present...

29:56.760 --> 30:00.196
the Possum Posse
Jamboree.

30:00.320 --> 30:02.117
Here it is.

30:04.440 --> 30:06.908
Oh, boy!
Just in time.

30:12.000 --> 30:16.198
Howdy, folks.
Who's your favourite possum?

30:16.320 --> 30:18.595
Lester!

30:20.240 --> 30:22.595
Got us a seat
right up front.

30:22.720 --> 30:24.358
Let me introduce you
to the posse.

30:24.480 --> 30:28.029
Here's Beuford, Beulah
and Mordachai.

30:29.560 --> 30:33.075
Hey, Lester, ready for yodelin'?
Ha-ha-ha.

30:33.200 --> 30:35.270
Sure am, Beuford!

30:35.400 --> 30:37.994
# Now gather 'round my possum pals
