30:56.080 --> 30:59.152
# Lester's Possum Park #
# Yodel-lay-ee ooo-ooo-ooo #

31:07.920 --> 31:10.912
# Don't you wanna be
A- hangin' from a tree #

31:11.040 --> 31:15.716
# We're mighty glad to see ya
And the parking's always free #

31:15.840 --> 31:19.071
# Here at Lester's
Po-Po #

31:19.200 --> 31:22.636
# Po-Possum Park #

31:22.760 --> 31:24.990
# Doodle-do
Diddle-do ##

31:28.640 --> 31:30.471
Hey, that's the ticket!

31:30.600 --> 31:33.353
I'll be right back,
my little possum pal.

31:33.480 --> 31:35.948
My life's a living...

31:36.080 --> 31:37.832
Hello,
little buddy!

31:39.320 --> 31:42.118
Who's your
favourite possum?

31:42.240 --> 31:44.117
Don't touch me.

31:44.240 --> 31:47.516
Aw. Why such
a long face?

31:47.640 --> 31:50.279
You're so sad.

31:50.400 --> 31:53.392
I know! You need
a big hug from Lester.

31:53.520 --> 31:55.750
- Don't even think about it! Agh! No!
- See?

31:55.880 --> 31:59.509
Now you feel
all good inside.

31:59.640 --> 32:01.710
Beat it, doofus!

32:05.720 --> 32:09.235
- Oh, no. No, Dad. Not that. Please.
- Here you go, sport.

32:09.360 --> 32:11.237
What say we get
our picture taken?

32:14.160 --> 32:17.197
- You have got to be kidding.
- Oh, all right.

32:17.320 --> 32:19.709
But you're missin' out.

32:22.520 --> 32:24.351
Hiya, son!

32:26.400 --> 32:28.755
Hey, everyone!
Check out the dork!

32:28.880 --> 32:30.199
Say "sassafras."

32:30.320 --> 32:32.595
Sassy-frass!

32:32.720 --> 32:36.030
Screech!

32:36.160 --> 32:38.151
Ahh! Get it! Get it!

32:41.920 --> 32:44.354
That's the spirit,
Maxie!

32:45.360 --> 32:47.590
Whoa! No!

32:47.720 --> 32:50.109
Dad, stop! Please!
No!

32:50.240 --> 32:52.435
Dad, look,
this is embarrassing.

32:52.560 --> 32:54.676
No, no, no!

32:54.800 --> 32:56.791
Let go! Dad!

33:00.720 --> 33:04.429
It's dork and dork, junior!

33:25.080 --> 33:27.753
- Agh!
- Max!

33:27.880 --> 33:30.030
Hey, what the heck
you tryin' to do?

33:30.160 --> 33:33.596
- Trying to get away from you!
- Me?

33:33.720 --> 33:36.109
- What'd I do?
- Forget it!

33:36.240 --> 33:38.993
I thought we was having fun.
What's the matter?

33:39.120 --> 33:41.873
Nothin'.
Let's just go.

33:42.000 --> 33:43.877
Well, come on!

33:54.240 --> 33:56.037
Hey, you dropped
your hat.

33:56.160 --> 33:58.913
Aah! This is
the stupidest vacation!

33:59.040 --> 34:01.270
You drag me from home,
you jam me in this dumb car,

34:01.400 --> 34:05.712
then drive me a million miles away
to see some stupid rat show!

34:05.840 --> 34:08.149
Call me when
the trip's over.

34:53.159 --> 34:57.790
Hey, Max. You wanna get in
some fishin' practise?

34:57.920 --> 35:01.310
Just a couple of days
'til we get to Lake Destiny.

35:01.440 --> 35:04.193
Maybe later.

35:37.080 --> 35:40.675
Whoa!
Now that's camping.

35:40.800 --> 35:43.394
Did you say somethin',
Max? Ow!

35:48.880 --> 35:50.871
- Pete?
- Goofy?

35:51.000 --> 35:54.754
Oh-ho!
What a serendipity doo-dah!

35:54.880 --> 35:57.075
Who'd've thunk it, huh?
Ha-ha.

35:57.200 --> 36:00.078
- Is P.J. Here?
- Who? Oh, yeah.

36:00.200 --> 36:02.350
I'm sure he's loafin'
around here somewhere.

36:02.480 --> 36:06.473
# It ain't a question of how
Just a matter of when #

36:06.600 --> 36:09.398
- # You get the message
that I'm trying to sing #
- Ooh, ooh, that baby.

36:09.520 --> 36:12.478
# I'm under a spell
I'm in over my head #

36:12.600 --> 36:16.912
- # And you know I'm goin'
all of the way to the end #
- What a goob!

36:17.040 --> 36:20.589
# To stand out
above the crowd #

36:20.720 --> 36:23.314
# Even if you got
to shout out loud #

36:23.440 --> 36:25.635
# No matter what the look is
Max, I get... #

36:25.760 --> 36:27.079
- Max!
- H-H-Hey!

36:27.200 --> 36:29.395
Whoa!
Small wilderness, dude.

36:29.520 --> 36:32.034
- Didn't expect to run into you.
- Apparently not.

36:32.160 --> 36:35.357
You're just jealous, man,
'cause you ain't got the moves!

36:35.480 --> 36:37.277
Yeah, you can
keep the moves.

