36:54.720 --> 36:57.359
You are gonna be famous,
buddy.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.516
Especially
with Roxanne.

36:59.640 --> 37:04.077
There's, uh, only one person
who doesn't know about it yet, Peej.

37:04.200 --> 37:06.668
